RUNTIME — Python dependencies (LiteLLM proxy venv)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The LiteLLM proxy bundled with ClawNex uses an isolated Python venv installed
on the host at install time. The deploy script (`deploy/install-prod.sh`)
creates the venv and runs:

  pip install "litellm[proxy]==1.83.0"
  pip install "httpx==0.28.1"

